#: .\manager\templates\public\about.html:313
msgid "知识与生活的一站式平台"
msgstr "One-stop platform for knowledge and life"

#: .\manager\templates\public\about.html:314
msgid ""
"我们是一支充满激情的团队，致力于打造集图书、在线课程、生活商品于一体的综合性数字平台。从电子书下载到在线学习，从生鲜超市到多元市场，让知识与便利触手可及。"
msgstr ""
"We are a passionate team dedicated to building an integrated digital "
"platform that combines books, online courses, and lifestyle products. From "
"e-book downloads to online learning, from fresh supermarket to diverse "
"market, making knowledge and convenience within reach."

#: .\manager\templates\public\about.html:331
msgid "成立年份"
msgstr "Year founded"

#: .\manager\templates\public\about.html:335
msgid "我们的故事"
msgstr "Our story"

#: .\manager\templates\public\about.html:336
msgid "从图书管理到综合平台"
msgstr "From book management to integrated platform"

#: .\manager\templates\public\about.html:337
msgid "最初，我们只是一个简单的DUNO 360。随着用户需求的增长，我们逐步拓展为一个集图书电商、在线教育、生活超市和多元市场于一体的综合性平台。"
msgstr ""
"Initially, we were just a simple DUNO 360. As user demand grew, we gradually"
" expanded into a comprehensive platform that integrates book e-commerce, "
"online education, a lifestyle supermarket, and a diverse marketplace."

#: .\manager\templates\public\about.html:338
msgid "如今，用户可以在我们的平台上购买并下载电子书、学习在线视频课程、选购各类商品，并通过智能AI助手获取即时帮助。我们用技术连接知识与生活。"
msgstr ""
"Today, users can purchase and download e-books, study online video courses, "
"shop for various products, and receive instant help from an intelligent AI "
"assistant on our platform. We use technology to connect knowledge and life."

